    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ultra Cop </strong>is a short and challenging old-school first/third-person action game taking loving inspiration from the 90's greats on both PC and consoles of the time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the not too distant future, South Africa enters the second Crime War. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As an enhanced Ultra Cop you are tasked with bringing down gangs and syndicates alike.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274790/extras/c7726fb83765f3a16789e361a789c99e.avif?t=1752588572\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274790/extras_big/c7726fb83765f3a16789e361a789c99e.avif?t=1752588572 width=800 height=226 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You're not here to arrest anyone. The protocol is simple: <strong>ZERO TOLERANCE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Law &amp; Order has fallen, and you have to pick it up. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Clean the streets, one bullet at a time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use an array of weapons ranging from the Battle Mech, Riot Car and future firepower to destroy all criminal elements and their operations.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274790/extras/6a25a88ed99f12cb9b8261ca16fbd709.avif?t=1752588572\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3274790/extras_big/6a25a88ed99f12cb9b8261ca16fbd709.avif?t=1752588572 width=800 height=226 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ultra Cop</strong> aims to provide a classic action experience from the 6th Generation of gaming, hearkening back to a time when gaming was simpler. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A quick pickup and play experience, designed to be completed within a single sitting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FEATURES:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four unique scenarios with multiple objectives and threat types</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Intense action with visceral effects</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pick up enemies/objects and throw them into hazards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rescue innocent babes!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Switch between first and third person perspectives</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Distinct Y2K gaming aesthetic from 1999</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Command friendly squad AI </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Four unique and era appropriate Soundtracks to choose from</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shorter format with an emphasis on replayability</p></li></ul>",
